Effective Date: 14/09/2025

Flippy Bird ("the Game", "we", "our", "us") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard information when you use our mobile game.

1. Information We Collect

When you use Flippy Bird, we may collect the following information:

Account Information: Your Google Play Games account ID and display name, used for authentication and leaderboard features.

Gameplay Data: Your highest scores for different game modes, stored in Firebase to display in leaderboards.

Device Information: General device information (such as device model, operating system version, and country) collected by analytics or advertising services.

Advertising Data: We use Google AdMob to serve ads, which may collect data such as device identifiers, cookies, and usage information for personalized or non-personalized ads.

2. How We Use Information

We use the collected information to:

Authenticate your account with Google Play Games.

Store and update your best scores in Firebase leaderboards.

Display global leaderboards and rankings.

Improve gameplay experience and fix bugs.

Show ads to support free access to the Game.

3. Sharing of Information

We do not sell or rent your personal data. We only share limited information with:

Google Play Games Services for login and leaderboard features.

Firebase for securely storing and updating scores.

Google AdMob for serving advertisements.

These third-party services may collect and process data according to their own privacy policies.

4. User Choices

If you do not log in with Google Play Games, you will not have access to the leaderboards.

You can disable personalized ads through your device settings.

You may request deletion of your leaderboard data by contacting us.

5. Children‚Äôs Privacy

Flippy Bird is not directed at children under 13. If you are under 13, please do not use the Game without parental consent.

6. Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. However, no system is 100% secure.

7. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted within the Game or app store listing with a new ‚ÄúEffective Date.‚Äù

